Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Major General Karen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,was against the New Himuka Government's method?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be more that we don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,about Karen's true intention
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and his...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A large number of Others\Nare invading Central Suoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminate the enemies at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But our defense system is not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Psynet is offline too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the council?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be... Arahabaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, how did it turn into this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will get it back this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?\NDon't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Psynet is offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, stay alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Arahabaki that was controlling\NSuoh is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what caused it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But the defense system has stopped working.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others are using this opening to invade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Wataru. What is going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm contacting you via telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see if I can get psynet back online.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka already went out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran garrison has got\Nthe headquarters surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, eliminate the Others as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This could likely be a coup d'état!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He contacted me via telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Arahabki is offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That caused psynet\Nand the defense system to go offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a coup d'état.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A coup d'état?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Major General Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They even went this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, if Major General Karen\Nis plotting a coup d'état...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:05:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,KAREN'S BETRAYAL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,About your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to meet up\Nwith Chairman Sumeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito must be worried about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to carry out his duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost contact with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the jamming signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost contact with the whole army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have pulled this off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Connected. Casting the image now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Via traffic cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we found the image before\Nthe jamming signal cut us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"SEIRAN FORCE"\NIt's the Seiran Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for interrupting, Chief Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The backup of psynet and\Nother online data is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, the Seiran garrison\Nhas us surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The underground evacuation route...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How likely are the enemies going to spot us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the OSF is now\Ndivided into two factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the council?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't managed to get a hold
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of Chairman Sumeragi's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you launching a coup,\NMajor General Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who terminated the Other in one strike
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No.1 of the Septentrion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain Eater Major General Karen Travers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The nation is under the constant invasion\Nof the Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The scouted soldiers\Nwho possess outstanding power
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and volunteer soldiers who train extensively\Nto hone their power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,must work as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we combine all of our strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Yuito Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already making headlines\Nright after your enlistment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Make use of the media's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The more fame you gather,\Nthe faster you get promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Joining Seto Platoon\Nwill help you learn better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Karen has had his eyes on you\Nsince you were still a cadet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The No.1 of the Septentrion expects\Ngreat things from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was Nagi acting so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the government do something to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What could have made Major General Karen\Ngo as far as to launching a coup?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Father must know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which platoon do you belong now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... We...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto was killed in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto was killed in action?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Is your commanding officer Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki, allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No other member was summoned\Nexcept for Gemma, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you've joined hands with Yuito\Nand the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not on Karen's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sum up the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. We need more soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you belong to my platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got a hold of the whole situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All we are certain for now is that\Nmembers of OSF have defected to Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They were instigated by Karen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and laid waste to the whole Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocent lives were caught up in this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is leading the civilians to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have another mission for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure Chairman Sumeragi\Nand the council members are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chairman and members of the council\Nweren't evacuated immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They are still on their way to a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OSF and the National Defense Forces\Nare en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But we lost contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a relief for the Chairman\Nif you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all members of OSF are on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seiran garrison isn't making a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they buying time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen has trapped us in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is his motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have got out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is like a ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the world people\Nwithout power see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bell Peppers can't connect to psynet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Luka!\N-Have you located Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't found anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he planning now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't contact Kagero and Kyoka either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Is everything online again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Major General Karen!\N-Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Blinded citizens of New Himuka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the foolish people who choose\Nto ignore the harsh side of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Karen Travers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Objecting the New Himuka administration\Nand its conducts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,has opened my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Is everything back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Master Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Blinded citizens of New Himuka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the foolish people who choose\Nto ignore the harsh side of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Karen Travers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Objecting the New Himuka administration\Nand its conducts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,has opened my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My comrades and I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,have formed an alliance with the Seiran garrison\Nwho share our vision and goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitiful citizens of New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept the reality before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This country has gone insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Himuka Government
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,move society forward\Nwith the integration of psynet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As we all know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the heart of psynet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is Arahabaki, the city-size computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost everyone in this country\Nand people with power
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,have their brains connected to Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives you the convenience of browsing and\Nusing all sorts of functions and information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You led a life of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is not true freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The government has\Naccess to all the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The citizens are being monitored like cattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to face this fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,are only alive for the benefit\Nof this country and its government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They silence anyone that will\Nchallenge the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They change the people's personalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,making the people their loyal pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They turn the people into their faithful cattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Himuka Government\Ndoesn't deserve our trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to stand up and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to overthrow this government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, go to Chairman Sumeragi at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the enemies to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes,\Npeople of the New Himuka Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of Seiran will defend\Nthe right to free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We will provide the people\Nwith the rights they deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All those who are willing to follow my cause
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,will not require any qualification.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others are headed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to the shelter where the Chairman
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and the council members are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you say about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to join OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power compatibility is too low.\NSo you can stop daydreaming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact you haven't been scouted\Nproves my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just have to join\Nas a volunteer soldier and accept my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove my worth to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever consider
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what your mother would say\Nif she was still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she would be proud of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the government did to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,he is still my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your enlistment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still against this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure not to get yourself hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're now a member of OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you can hold your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to use this chance to talk about\Nour family and your late mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We should ask Kaito to join us\Nfor dinner next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I stand at Seiran's frontline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against the notion of being controlled\Nby a handful of powerful men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, Seiran is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will crumble New Himuka's system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will break free from the control of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a war of our revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have opened their eyes\Nand those who wish to see the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Over here!\N-Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we will strike down
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka's corrupted system!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A TOMORROW OF RUIN
